-install Live Server => open with Live server

-script can be placed in head or body
-ideally end of body
Reason: browser execute html top to bottom
        JS takes time to parse and execute
        rendering takes some time
        bad user experience

        mostly JS code deal with html component.
        By having it in the end of the body, it's ensured
        all elements are shown before doing something
        on them

can run js file in node also: node index.js

no two types of number: only number (no float, no integer)

undefined is a primitive type and a fixed value also

different types of object can be saved in arrays

array's dimension is dynamic